ousel_Region_0&lid=ARTICLE_15598482_Polish_President_Lech_Kaczynski_Killed_When_Plane_Crashed_On_Approach_To_Smolensk_Airport_In_Russia|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据报道，飞机机翼撞上树梢，落到地面，然后解体并迅速开始燃烧。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5hKIo35KuaQYuIFCc2fdArySMvvng|title=Polish president's plane crashes in Russia: ministry|publisher=AFP|language=en|accessdate=2010-04-10|archive-date=2010-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100413184312/http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5hKIo35KuaQYuIFCc2fdArySMvvng|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

